name: Kings of the Runic Console
description: There are Rootmason carvings all over the heirlooms of the Kings of the Runic Console. Why? How? They also capture moonlight in a moonlight condenser - old technology created by the Gibbun in order to distill moonlight for further processing. Now armed with knowledge of the stars, moons, and tides, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
